  "description": "Oh GOD, not another GAY-ass show... Inherently Disordered is a one-man comedy show of Aldrick’s experiences studying in Montreal, living in Toronto, and working in Chicago. He details a crisis of faith trying to reconcile Catholicism with his sexuality. (But funny!)",
