  "website": "",
  "plain_language": "Inherently Disordered is a one-man comedy show of Aldrick’s experiences studying in Montreal, living in Toronto, and working in Chicago. Aldrick recounts his journey in coming to terms with his queerness. He details a crisis of faith trying to reconcile Catholicism with his sexuality. Although some of the themes can be deep and dark, it is told with a sense of humor that alternates between whimsical and observational to biting and political.",
